  70,28,Achiika! B…õ Duuma (Naawuni) daazaaba ka yőĶmbahiga
  70,29,Ni ninvu…£u shőĶba ban gu b…õ tooni
  70,30,"Na…£ila b…õ daamiliya pa…£aba, ni b…õ dabpa…£aba. Achiika! Bannim‚Äô maa pala b…õ ni galindi sh…õba"
  70,31,"Amaa! Ninvu…£u so Ňčun ti bo (pa…£a shőĶba) din nyaaŇča, t…Ē! Bannim‚Äô maa n- ny…õ ban kpahi yőĶ…£i tariga"
  70,32,"Ni ninvu…£u shőĶba ban guri b…õ da- amaananima, n-ti pahi b…õ daalikauli"
